	<content><![CDATA[const pipeFunctions = (...fns) => fns.reduce((f, g) => (...args) => g(f(...args)));]]></content>
	<description>Performs left-to-right function composition.  Use `Array.reduce()` with the spread operator (`...`) to perform left-to-right function composition. The first (leftmost) function can accept one or more arguments; the remaining functions must be unary.</description>
